---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms Of Use"
  description="Terms of Use for QuizNiva."
  currentPath="/terms"
>
  <section class="page-intro section">
    <p class="eyebrow">Terms</p>
    <h1>Terms Of Use</h1>
    <p>Last updated: May 19, 2026</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section prose prose--standalone">
    <h2>Educational Use</h2>
    <p>
      QuizNiva provides notes, examples, quizzes, and explanations for learning and practice. The content is not a guarantee of exam results.
    </p>

    <h2>Accuracy</h2>
    <p>
      We aim to keep explanations accurate and beginner-friendly. Learners should verify important information with teachers, official documentation, or trusted references.
    </p>

    <h2>User Responsibility</h2>
    <p>
      Use the site honestly for study. Do not misuse quizzes, attempt to disrupt the site, or copy content without permission.
    </p>

    <h2>Advertising</h2>
    <p>
      The first version does not include ads. If advertising is added later, it should not be treated as part of the quiz or learning content.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
